tome book~
   Greetings, Those of stout heart and perservence should find a welcome in
the lands here. For those heros are needed to fight the battle of Good...
and of Evil. You will learn from heros that are now holding the battle
lines. You will learn by the doing and the success or failure of that
doing. You will learn... or perish.
   For those truly new to this realm called Duris, then a helping hand may
come as a welcome to some. The best help anyone can give is knowledge and
within these pages there is a bit of that knowledge. To read and to learn
will help you in the days and months to come. Come! READ PAGE1
~
